        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en-us">classification_scheme_item_relationship_categorization</rdfs:label>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="en-us">records the bindings of zero, one or more instances of the Classification_Scheme_Item_Relationships (10.3.3) class with exactly one instance of the Classification_Scheme_Item_Relationship_Type class.
This association records the categorization, as modelled by the instance of the Classification_Scheme_Item_Relationship_Type class, of the relationship between the subject and object sets of classification scheme items that is modelled by the instance of the Classification_Scheme_Item_Relationship class.</skos:definition>
