        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">Identifier Scope</rdfs:label>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">association that records the binding of zero, one or more instances of the Scoped_Identifier (7.3.2) class with exactly one instance of the Namespace (7.3.3) class which provides the scope for the instance of the Scoped_Identifier. The association records the namespace that provides the scope for the scoped identifiers.</skos:definition>
