        <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">Registry Item</skos:prefLabel>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">A registry item is recorded in the registry, but is not necessarily identified, named, defined, classified, registered or administered. Specific information needs to be provided for each of these categories which can be provided when the item is initially recorded, or later. See also classified item (3.2.59), identified item (3.2.61), registered item (3.2.65), administered item (3.2.66) and attached item (3.2.68).</skos:scopeNote>
    </owl:Class>
